### Description:
This is a simple Instagram bot that generates random Instagram captions based on a given hashtag.

### Usage:
1. Input the hashtag you want to generate captions for.
2. The bot will generate a random caption based on the hashtag you provided.
3. Copy and paste the generated caption into your Instagram post.

### Instructions:
1. Open the terminal and navigate to the directory where you saved the bot.
2. Run the following command to install the dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`.
3. Run the following command to start the bot: `python main.py`.
4. Input the hashtag you want to generate captions for.
5. The bot will generate a random caption based on the hashtag you provided.
6. Copy and paste the generated caption into your Instagram post.

### Output:
The bot will generate a random caption based on the hashtag you provided.

### Credits:
This bot was created by [InstagramBot](https://github.com/InstagramBot) and is based on the [Instagram Caption Generator](https://github.com/InstagramBot/Instagram-Caption-Generator) project.

### License:

### Disclaimer:
This bot is intended for educational and entertainment purposes only. It is not intended to be used for spamming or any other illegal activities.

### Contact:
If you have any questions or issues with the bot, please feel free to contact me via email at [your_email_here] or through the GitHub issue tracker. </s>
